COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 1:04PM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 26.5 thousand have died.

In the last day, 291 new infections were reported and 3 deaths. This is trending upwards.

Fortunately, 45.6 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 79.6% have their 1st shot and 57.2% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 7.3 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~21 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ will have the first dose by Dec-07 and fully vaccinated by 2022-Jan-04. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
